This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with semantic segmentation of point clouds for urban scene understanding. The use of mobile LiDAR systems also suggests that it could belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of deep learning models, which could place it in the Machine Learning (cs.LG) or Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the focus on urban mapping and scene understanding could also suggest the Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
